text: Asyraf is a Malay given name. Notable people with this given name include: * Amar Asyraf (born 1986), Malaysian actor * Amirul Asyraf Suhaidi (born 1994), Malaysian football player * Asyraf Wajdi Dusuki (born 1976), Malaysian politician * Famirul Asyraf Sayuti (born 1989), Malaysian football player * Khairul Asyraf (born 1994), Malaysian football player * Muhd Asyraf Azan (born 1988), Malaysian squash player
title: Asyraf
